meta.text_editor: This demo shows how the Google Places Autocomplete functionality can be used to automatically populate address fields and a Google Map. It shows all available outputs from the Google Map field. A Google API key must first be entered into the WS Form settings 'Advanced' tab. The countries searched can be limited by choosing countries in the Google Address field settings under  'Advanced' in the 'Restrictions' section.
